<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Reset Your Password - IntelliCampus</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .reset-code {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      display: block;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Reset Your IntelliCampus Password</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= user.firstName %>,</p>
      <p>It seems like you’ve requested to reset your password. No worries, we’ve got you covered! Use the following code to reset your password:</p>
      <div class="reset-code">
        <%= resetCode %>
      </div>
      <p>Simply enter this code on the password reset page to proceed.</p>
      <p>If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email—your password will remain unchanged.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Need any further help? Feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@IntelliCampus.com">support@IntelliCampus.com</a>.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The IntelliCampus Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
